videos.description: Jrue Holiday gets ahead of the defense twice and puts in a couple layups to get on the board for Milwaukee.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Holiday gets out in transition twice for his first 2 buckets as a Buck) 2020/12/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Holiday gets out in transition twice for his first 2 buckets as a Buck

videos.description: The Bucks get a turnover and Khris Middleton tries to throw a behind-the-back pass but it's blocked and it ends up with Donte Divincenzo who finds Giannis Antetokounmpo for the dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Broken play leads to Giannis dunk) 2020/12/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Broken play leads to Giannis dunk

videos.description: Jaylen Brown swats the ball off the backboard sending the Celtics on a fastbreak which ends in Semi Ojeleye finishing the bucket plus the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Brown’s block leads to the Ojeleye and-1) 2020/12/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brown's block leads to the Ojeleye and-1

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo skies high for the huge rejection on Grant Williams.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis comes out of nowhere for the block) 2020/12/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis comes out of nowhere for the block

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo expands his range to behind the 3-point line as he knocks down the long-range jumper.
videos.headline: Giannis drains the stepback 3

videos.description: Marcus Smart knocks the ball loose from Giannis Antetokounmpo and throws it ahead to Jayson Tatum who finishes with the layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Smart strips Giannis to set up a Tatum layup) 2020/12/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Smart strips Giannis to set up a Tatum layup

videos.description: Jayson Tatum drives the lane and it looks like he's throwing the pass to Daniel Theis but it ends up falling in the hoop for 2.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tatum impresses with acrobatic bucket) 2020/12/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tatum impresses with acrobatic bucket

videos.description: Jayson Tatum scores eight quick points at the end of the third quarter to extend the Celtics' lead.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tatum gets hot at the end of the third) 2020/12/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tatum gets hot at the end of the third

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo splits the double team and throws the no-look dime to Donte DiVoncenzo for the layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis shows off handles, drops dime to DiVoncenzo) 2020/12/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis shows off handles, drops dime to DiVoncenzo

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo cooks the Celtics knocking down shots from all over the court cutting Boston's lead to two and forcing them to call timeout.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis' flurry forces a Celtics timeout) 2020/12/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis' flurry forces a Celtics timeout

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo is fouled with less than a second to play with a chance to tie, but he splits the free throws resulting in a loss.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis misses game-tying free throw in final seconds) 2020/12/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis misses game-tying free throw in final seconds

videos.description: Jayson Tatum banks the three over Giannis Antetokounmpo giving the Celtics the two-point lead with less than a second remaining.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tatum banks in 3, giving Celtics late lead) 2020/12/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tatum banks in 3, giving Celtics late lead

videos.description: Jayson Tatum banks in a 3-pointer over Giannis Antetokounmpo, giving Boston the lead with under a second remaining. Antetokounmpo is fouled on the next possession but splits the free throws, resulting in a loss.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Celtics-Bucks concludes in wild finish) 2020/12/23 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Celtics-Bucks concludes in wild finish
